+## capture browser
+
+Captures a public or local URL into a memory record.
+
+```text
+python pala.py capture browser --url http://127.0.0.1:8765
+```
+
+Useful options:
+
+| Option | Purpose |
+|---|---|
+| `--title "..."` | Set record title |
+| `--project trugurpala/pala-memory-core` | Link captured page to a project |
+| `--tag dashboard` | Add extra tag |
+| `--max-chars 12000` | Limit text stored in the record |
+| `--timeout 20` | Set request timeout |
+
+This first browser connector fetches URLs directly. Authenticated browser-session capture and screenshots are planned as a later Playwright/Chrome connector.
+
 ## dashboard serve
 
 Starts a local dashboard server from the `dashboard/` folder.
