+## Browser Capture Defaults
+
+`pala capture browser` fetches the requested URL directly. It does not yet use logged-in browser sessions or bypass access controls.
+
+| Control | Purpose |
+|---|---|
+| `--max-bytes` | Limit downloaded response size |
+| `--max-chars` | Limit stored text |
+| `--timeout` | Avoid hanging on slow pages |
+| `--project` | Link capture to a project |
